description:
Palm Canyon is one of a number of trails in Agua Caliente Tribal Preserve near Palm Springs.
Varied topography, it's mountains and desert.  Stop at the visitor centre for a trail map and trail information. There is a fee for entry into the tribal preserve.
http://indian-canyons.com/Palm.html
directions: From Palm Springs, south on Palm Canyon drive to the visitor center.
title: Palm Canyon - Victor trail
